headline: Eric Trump shares photo of woman sitting next to him on flight wearing a “Let's Go Brandon” Shirt
sentences:
pic.twitter.com/yHLJkbXoRQ
— Eric Trump (@EricTrump) April 13, 2022
Rep. Jim Jordan tweeted recently:
Eric Trump: “If I did 1/100 of what Hunter Biden did, I’d be in jail.”
He’s not wrong.
Wednesday, Eric Trump shared a photo of a woman sitting next to him on a flight wearing a “Lets’ Go Brandon” shirt.

pic.twitter.com/7LNVzcAZJs
— Eric Trump (@EricTrump) March 17, 2022
— Eric Trump (@EricTrump) March 20, 2022
Let’s also remember that @Twitter suspended @nypost for this very same story.
The awesome woman sitting next to me on a flight… I’m in good company!
Americans have had it with the double standard.
